  "description": "Very large grains (420ms Gaussian window) at low density (8 grains/sec). With 12 voices, total grain rate is approximately 96 grains/minute — massively overlapping. Grains blur into each other in long cross-fades. The most pad-like behavior OPAL can produce. Position slowly wandering through 4-second buffer. Temporal structure erased.",
